# Code owners — GitHub auto-requests these accounts for review on matching paths.
#
# This template ships with NO active owners so it works for anyone who clones or
# "Use this template"s it (uncommented placeholder owners would raise "unknown
# owner" errors). Uncomment and replace OWNER with real GitHub usernames/teams
# (e.g. @your-org/maintainers) when you adopt the repo.

# Default owner for everything
# *                 @OWNER

# Workflow & policy files warrant extra care
# /.github/         @OWNER
# /CLAUDE.md        @OWNER
# /AGENTS.md        @OWNER
# /VERSIONING.md    @OWNER
# /scripts/         @OWNER
